  "lore": {
    "key": "Tbl_Unit_Desc_76",
    "english": "A UFS Anti-Demon soldier. Lost her right arm in a battle against demons and is now armed with a specialized android arm. Polite and composed, she rarely expresses her emotions and carries out her duties calmly.\n\nHer weapon syncs with her android arm, allowing her to manipulate gravity. It transforms between a sword and a gun. When in sword form, it cuts enemies with ten times greater force than what a human can produce, and when it is a gun, it fires bullets with a repulsive force.",
    "japanese": "A UFS Anti-Demon soldier. Lost her right arm in a battle against demons and is now armed with a specialized android arm. Polite and composed, she rarely expresses her emotions and carries out her duties calmly.\n\nHer weapon syncs with her android arm, allowing her to manipulate gravity. It transforms between a sword and a gun. When in sword form, it cuts enemies with ten times greater force than what a human can produce, and when it is a gun, it fires bullets with a repulsive force.",
    "korean": "A UFS Anti-Demon soldier. Lost her right arm in a battle against demons and is now armed with a specialized android arm. Polite and composed, she rarely expresses her emotions and carries out her duties calmly.\n\nHer weapon syncs with her android arm, allowing her to manipulate gravity. It transforms between a sword and a gun. When in sword form, it cuts enemies with ten times greater force than what a human can produce, and when it is a gun, it fires bullets with a repulsive force.",
    "chinese_simplified": "A UFS Anti-Demon soldier. Lost her right arm in a battle against demons and is now armed with a specialized android arm. Polite and composed, she rarely expresses her emotions and carries out her duties calmly.\n\nHer weapon syncs with her android arm, allowing her to manipulate gravity. It transforms between a sword and a gun. When in sword form, it cuts enemies with ten times greater force than what a human can produce, and when it is a gun, it fires bullets with a repulsive force.",
    "chinese_traditional": "A UFS Anti-Demon soldier. Lost her right arm in a battle against demons and is now armed with a specialized android arm. Polite and composed, she rarely expresses her emotions and carries out her duties calmly.\n\nHer weapon syncs with her android arm, allowing her to manipulate gravity. It transforms between a sword and a gun. When in sword form, it cuts enemies with ten times greater force than what a human can produce, and when it is a gun, it fires bullets with a repulsive force.",
    "spanish": "A UFS Anti-Demon soldier. Lost her right arm in a battle against demons and is now armed with a specialized android arm. Polite and composed, she rarely expresses her emotions and carries out her duties calmly.\n\nHer weapon syncs with her android arm, allowing her to manipulate gravity. It transforms between a sword and a gun. When in sword form, it cuts enemies with ten times greater force than what a human can produce, and when it is a gun, it fires bullets with a repulsive force."
  },
